---
title: "Page Stack"
description: "A card-stack navigation pattern with layered pages that fan, peek, and collapse."
createdAt: "2026-02"
category: "exploration"
type: "interactive"
---

A card-stack navigation pattern where pages are layered cards that fan open, peek on hover, and collapse into a tight stack. Each card links to others through inline mentions, building a non-linear reading experience.
